Description: The NIH data sharing policy is catalyzing data science and informatics innovation in translational cancer research and biomedical discovery. The speakers bring three diverse perspectives from data science, public health and biomedical informatics to the cancer research community. Join us in a SWOT analysis of how data sharing can catalyze more effective and impactful innovation in this important aspect of translational cancer research.
